{"chapter_number":54,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":37,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"القمر","name_complex":"Al-Qamar","name_simple":"Al-Qamar","verses_count":55,"pages":[528,531],"meaning":{"text":"The Moon","en":"The Moon","id":"Bulan"},"verses":[[[1,4847,"54:1","اقْتَرَبَتِ السَّاعَةُ وَانشَقَّ الْقَمَرُ",["The hour drew nigh and the moon did rend asunder.","Saat (hari Kiamat) semakin dekat, bulan pun terbelah."],528,27,53,211,null,null],[2,4848,"54:2","وَإِن يَرَوْا آيَةً يُعْرِضُوا وَيَقُولُوا سِحْرٌ مُّسْتَمِرٌّ",["And if they see a miracle they turn aside and say: Transient magic.","Dan jika mereka (orang-orang musyrikin) melihat suatu tanda (mukjizat), mereka berpaling dan berkata, “(Ini adalah) sihir yang terus menerus.”"],528,27,53,211,null,null],[3,4849,"54:3","وَكَذَّبُوا وَاتَّبَعُوا أَهْوَاءَهُمْ ۚ وَكُلُّ أَمْرٍ مُّسْتَقِرٌّ",["And they call (it) a lie, and follow their low desires; and every affair has its appointed term.","Dan mereka mendustakan (Muhammad) dan mengikuti keinginannya, padahal setiap urusan telah ada ketetapannya."],528,27,53,211,null,null],[4,4850,"54:4","وَلَقَدْ جَاءَهُم مِّنَ الْأَنبَاءِ مَا فِيهِ مُزْدَجَرٌ",["And certainly some narratives have come to them wherein is prevention--","Dan sungguh, telah datang kepada mereka beberapa kisah yang di dalamnya terdapat ancaman (terhadap kekafiran),"],528,27,53,211,null,null],[5,4851,"54:5","حِكْمَةٌ بَالِغَةٌ ۖ فَمَا تُغْنِ النُّذُرُ",["Consummate wisdom-- but warnings do not avail;","(itulah) suatu hikmah yang sempurna, tetapi peringatan-peringatan itu tidak berguna (bagi mereka),"],528,27,53,211,null,null],[6,4852,"54:6","فَتَوَلَّ عَنْهُمْ ۘ يَوْمَ يَدْعُ الدَّاعِ إِلَىٰ شَيْءٍ نُّكُرٍ",["So turn (your) back on them (for) the day when the inviter shall invite them to a hard task,","maka berpalinglah engkau (Muhammad) dari mereka pada hari (ketika) penyeru (malaikat) mengajak (mereka) kepada sesuatu yang tidak menyenangkan (hari pembalasan),"],528,27,53,211,null,null],[7,4853,"54:7","خُشَّعًا أَبْصَارُهُمْ يَخْرُجُونَ مِنَ الْأَجْدَاثِ كَأَنَّهُمْ جَرَادٌ مُّنتَشِرٌ",["Their eyes cast down, going forth from their graves as if they were scattered locusts,","pandangan mereka tertunduk, ketika mereka keluar dari kuburan, seakan-akan mereka belalang yang beterbangan,"],529,27,53,211,null,null],[8,4854,"54:8","مُّهْطِعِينَ إِلَى الدَّاعِ ۖ يَقُولُ الْكَافِرُونَ هَٰذَا يَوْمٌ عَسِرٌ",["Hastening to the inviter. The unbelievers shall say: This is a hard day.","dengan patuh mereka segera datang kepada penyeru itu. Orang-orang kafir berkata, “Ini adalah hari yang sulit.”"],529,27,53,211,null,null],[9,4855,"54:9","كَذَّبَتْ قَبْلَهُمْ قَوْمُ نُوحٍ فَكَذَّبُوا عَبْدَنَا وَقَالُوا مَجْنُونٌ وَازْدُجِرَ",["Before them the people of Nuh rejected, so they rejected Our servant and called (him) mad, and he was driven away.","Sebelum mereka, kaum Nuh juga telah mendustakan (rasul), maka mereka mendustakan hamba Kami (Nuh) dan mengatakan, “Dia orang gila!” Lalu diusirnya dengan ancaman."],529,27,53,212,null,null],[10,4856,"54:10","فَدَعَا رَبَّهُ أَنِّي مَغْلُوبٌ فَانتَصِرْ",["Therefore he called upon his Lord: I am overcome, come Thou then to help.","Maka dia (Nuh) mengadu kepada Tuhannya, “Sesungguhnya aku telah dikalahkan, maka tolonglah (aku).”"],529,27,53,212,null,null],[11,4857,"54:11","فَفَتَحْنَا أَبْوَابَ السَّمَاءِ بِمَاءٍ مُّنْهَمِرٍ",["So We opened the gates of the cloud with water pouring","Lalu Kami bukakan pintu-pintu langit dengan (menurunkan) air yang tercurah,"],529,27,53,212,null,null],[12,4858,"54:12","وَفَجَّرْنَا الْأَرْضَ عُيُونًا فَالْتَقَى الْمَاءُ عَلَىٰ أَمْرٍ قَدْ قُدِرَ",["And We made water to flow forth in the land in springs, so the water gathered together according to a measure already ordained.","dan Kami jadikan bumi menyemburkan mata-mata air maka bertemulah (air-air) itu sehingga (meluap menimbulkan) keadaan (bencana) yang telah ditetapkan."],529,27,53,212,null,null],[13,4859,"54:13","وَحَمَلْنَاهُ عَلَىٰ ذَاتِ أَلْوَاحٍ وَدُسُرٍ",["And We bore him on that which was made of planks and nails","Dan Kami angkut dia (Nuh) ke atas (kapal) yang terbuat dari papan dan pasak,"],529,27,53,212,null,null],[14,4860,"54:14","تَجْرِي بِأَعْيُنِنَا جَزَاءً لِّمَن كَانَ كُفِرَ",["Sailing, before Our eyes, a reward for him who was denied.","yang berlayar dengan pemeliharaan (pengawasan) Kami sebagai balasan bagi orang yang telah diingkari (kaumnya)."],529,27,53,212,null,null],[15,4861,"54:15","وَلَقَد تَّرَكْنَاهَا آيَةً فَهَلْ مِن مُّدَّكِرٍ",["And certainly We left it as a sign, but is there anyone who","Dan sungguh, kapal itu telah Kami jadikan sebagai tanda (pelajaran). Maka adakah orang yang mau mengambil pelajaran?"],529,27,53,212,null,null],[16,4862,"54:16","فَكَيْفَ كَانَ عَذَابِي وَنُذُرِ",["How (great) was then My punishment and My warning!","Maka betapa dahsyatnya azab-Ku dan peringatan-Ku!"],529,27,53,212,null,null],[17,4863,"54:17","وَلَقَدْ يَسَّرْنَا الْقُرْآنَ لِلذِّكْرِ فَهَلْ مِن مُّدَّكِرٍ",["And certainly We have made the Quran easy for remembrance, but is there anyone who will mind?","Dan sungguh, telah Kami mudahkan Al-Qur'an untuk peringatan, maka adakah orang yang mau mengambil pelajaran?"],529,27,53,212,null,null],[18,4864,"54:18","كَذَّبَتْ عَادٌ فَكَيْفَ كَانَ عَذَابِي وَنُذُرِ",["Ad treated (the truth) as a lie, so how (great) was My punishment and My warning!","Kaum ‘Ad pun telah mendustakan. Maka betapa dahsyatnya azab-Ku dan peringatan-Ku!"],529,27,53,212,null,null],[19,4865,"54:19","إِنَّا أَرْسَلْنَا عَلَيْهِمْ رِيحًا صَرْصَرًا فِي يَوْمِ نَحْسٍ مُّسْتَمِرٍّ",["Surely We sent on them a tornado in a day of bitter ill-luck","Sesungguhnya Kami telah menghembuskan angin yang sangat kencang kepada mereka pada hari nahas yang terus menerus,"],529,27,53,212,null,null],[20,4866,"54:20","تَنزِعُ النَّاسَ كَأَنَّهُمْ أَعْجَازُ نَخْلٍ مُّنقَعِرٍ",["Tearing men away as if they were the trunks of palm-trees torn up.","yang membuat manusia bergelimpangan, mereka bagaikan pohon-pohon kurma yang tumbang dengan akar-akarnya."],529,27,53,212,null,null],[21,4867,"54:21","فَكَيْفَ كَانَ عَذَابِي وَنُذُرِ",["How (great) was then My punishment and My warning!","Maka betapa dahsyatnya azab-Ku dan peringatan-Ku!"],529,27,53,212,null,null],[22,4868,"54:22","وَلَقَدْ يَسَّرْنَا الْقُرْآنَ لِلذِّكْرِ فَهَلْ مِن مُّدَّكِرٍ",["And certainly We have made the Quran easy for remembrance, but is there anyone who will mind?","Dan sungguh, telah Kami mudahkan Al-Qur'an untuk peringatan, maka adakah orang yang mau mengambil pelajaran?"],529,27,53,212,null,null],[23,4869,"54:23","كَذَّبَتْ ثَمُودُ بِالنُّذُرِ",["Samood rejected the warning.","Kaum samud pun telah mendustakan peringatan itu."],529,27,53,212,null,null],[24,4870,"54:24","فَقَالُوا أَبَشَرًا مِّنَّا وَاحِدًا نَّتَّبِعُهُ إِنَّا إِذًا لَّفِي ضَلَالٍ وَسُعُرٍ",["So they said: What! a single mortal from among us! Shall we follow him? Most surely we shall in that case be in sure error and distress:","Maka mereka berkata, “Bagaimana kita akan mengikuti seorang manusia (biasa) di antara kita? Sungguh, kalau begitu kita benar-benar telah sesat dan gila."],529,27,53,212,null,null],[25,4871,"54:25","أَأُلْقِيَ الذِّكْرُ عَلَيْهِ مِن بَيْنِنَا بَلْ هُوَ كَذَّابٌ أَشِرٌ",["Has the reminder been made to light upon him from among us? Nay! he is an insolent liar!","Apakah wahyu itu diturunkan kepadanya di antara kita? Pastilah dia (Shalih) seorang yang sangat pendusta (dan) sombong.”"],529,27,53,212,null,null],[26,4872,"54:26","سَيَعْلَمُونَ غَدًا مَّنِ الْكَذَّابُ الْأَشِرُ",["Tomorrow shall they know who is the liar, the insolent one.","Kelak mereka akan mengetahui siapa yang sebenarnya sangat pendusta (dan) sombong itu."],529,27,53,212,null,null],[27,4873,"54:27","إِنَّا مُرْسِلُو النَّاقَةِ فِتْنَةً لَّهُمْ فَارْتَقِبْهُمْ وَاصْطَبِرْ",["Surely We are going to send the she-camel as a trial for them; therefore watch them and have patience.","Sesungguhnya Kami akan mengirimkan unta betina sebagai cobaan bagi mereka, maka tunggulah mereka dan bersabarlah (Shalih)."],529,27,53,212,null,null],[28,4874,"54:28","وَنَبِّئْهُمْ أَنَّ الْمَاءَ قِسْمَةٌ بَيْنَهُمْ ۖ كُلُّ شِرْبٍ مُّحْتَضَرٌ",["And inform them that the water is shared between them; every share of the water shall be regulated.","Dan beritahukanlah kepada mereka bahwa air itu dibagi di antara mereka (dengan unta betina itu); setiap orang berhak mendapat giliran minum."],530,27,53,212,null,null],[29,4875,"54:29","فَنَادَوْا صَاحِبَهُمْ فَتَعَاطَىٰ فَعَقَرَ",["But they called their companion, so he took (the sword) and slew (her).","Maka mereka memanggil kawannya, lalu dia menangkap (unta itu) dan memotongnya."],530,27,53,212,null,null],[30,4876,"54:30","فَكَيْفَ كَانَ عَذَابِي وَنُذُرِ",["How (great) was then My punishment and My warning!","Maka betapa dahsyatnya azab-Ku dan peringatan-Ku!"],530,27,53,212,null,null],[31,4877,"54:31","إِنَّا أَرْسَلْنَا عَلَيْهِمْ صَيْحَةً وَاحِدَةً فَكَانُوا كَهَشِيمِ الْمُحْتَظِرِ",["Surely We sent upon them a single cry, so they were like the dry fragments of trees which the maker of an enclosure collects.","Kami kirimkan atas mereka satu suara yang keras mengguntur, maka jadilah mereka seperti batang-batang kering yang lapuk."],530,27,53,212,null,null],[32,4878,"54:32","وَلَقَدْ يَسَّرْنَا الْقُرْآنَ لِلذِّكْرِ فَهَلْ مِن مُّدَّكِرٍ",["And certainly We have made the Quran easy for remembrance, but is there anyone who will mind?","Dan sungguh, telah Kami mudahkan Al-Qur'an untuk peringatan, maka adakah orang yang mau mengambil pelajaran?"],530,27,53,212,null,null],[33,4879,"54:33","كَذَّبَتْ قَوْمُ لُوطٍ بِالنُّذُرِ",["The people of Lut treated the warning. as a lie.","Kaum Luth pun telah mendustakan peringatan itu."],530,27,53,212,null,null],[34,4880,"54:34","إِنَّا أَرْسَلْنَا عَلَيْهِمْ حَاصِبًا إِلَّا آلَ لُوطٍ ۖ نَّجَّيْنَاهُم بِسَحَرٍ",["Surely We sent upon them a stonestorm, except Lut's followers; We saved them a little before daybreak,","Sesungguhnya Kami kirimkan kepada mereka badai yang membawa batu-batu (yang menimpa mereka), kecuali keluarga Luth. Kami selamatkan mereka sebelum fajar menyingsing,"],530,27,53,212,null,null],[35,4881,"54:35","نِّعْمَةً مِّنْ عِندِنَا ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ نَجْزِي مَن شَكَرَ",["A favor from Us; thus do We reward him who gives thanks.","sebagai nikmat dari Kami. Demikianlah Kami memberi balasan kepada orang-orang yang bersyukur."],530,27,53,212,null,null],[36,4882,"54:36","وَلَقَدْ أَنذَرَهُم بَطْشَتَنَا فَتَمَارَوْا بِالنُّذُرِ",["And certainly he warned them of Our violent seizure, but they obstinately disputed the warning.","Dan sungguh, dia (Luth) telah memperingatkan mereka akan hukuman Kami, tetapi mereka mendustakan peringatan-Ku."],530,27,53,212,null,null],[37,4883,"54:37","وَلَقَدْ رَاوَدُوهُ عَن ضَيْفِهِ فَطَمَسْنَا أَعْيُنَهُمْ فَذُوقُوا عَذَابِي وَنُذُرِ",["And certainly they endeavored to turn him from his guests, but We blinded their eyes; so taste My chastisement and My warning.","Dan sungguh, mereka telah membujuknya (agar menyerahkan) tamunya (kepada mereka), lalu Kami butakan mata mereka, maka rasakanlah azab-Ku dan peringatan-Ku!"],530,27,53,212,null,null],[38,4884,"54:38","وَلَقَدْ صَبَّحَهُم بُكْرَةً عَذَابٌ مُّسْتَقِرٌّ",["And certainly a lasting chastisement overtook them in the morning.","Dan sungguh, pada esok harinya mereka benar-benar ditimpa azab yang tetap."],530,27,53,212,null,null],[39,4885,"54:39","فَذُوقُوا عَذَابِي وَنُذُرِ",["So taste My chastisement and My warning.","Maka rasakanlah azab-Ku dan peringatan-Ku!"],530,27,53,212,null,null],[40,4886,"54:40","وَلَقَدْ يَسَّرْنَا الْقُرْآنَ لِلذِّكْرِ فَهَلْ مِن مُّدَّكِرٍ",["And certainly We have made the Quran easy for remembrance, but is there anyone who will mind?","Dan sungguh, telah Kami mudahkan Al-Qur'an untuk peringatan, maka adakah orang yang mau mengambil pelajaran?"],530,27,53,212,null,null],[41,4887,"54:41","وَلَقَدْ جَاءَ آلَ فِرْعَوْنَ النُّذُرُ",["And certainly the warning came to Firon's people.","Dan sungguh, peringatan telah datang kepada keluarga Fir‘aun."],530,27,53,212,null,null],[42,4888,"54:42","كَذَّبُوا بِآيَاتِنَا كُلِّهَا فَأَخَذْنَاهُمْ أَخْذَ عَزِيزٍ مُّقْتَدِرٍ",["They rejected all Our communications, so We overtook them after the manner of a Mighty, Powerful One.","Mereka mendustakan mukjizat-mukjizat Kami semuanya, maka Kami azab mereka dengan azab dari Yang Mahaperkasa, Mahakuasa."],530,27,53,212,null,null],[43,4889,"54:43","أَكُفَّارُكُمْ خَيْرٌ مِّنْ أُولَٰئِكُمْ أَمْ لَكُم بَرَاءَةٌ فِي الزُّبُرِ",["Are the unbelievers of yours better than these, or is there an exemption for you in the scriptures?","Apakah orang-orang kafir di lingkunganmu (kaum musyrikin) lebih baik dari mereka, ataukah kamu telah mempunyai jaminan kebebasan (dari azab) dalam kitab-kitab terdahulu?"],530,27,53,212,null,null],[44,4890,"54:44","أَمْ يَقُولُونَ نَحْنُ جَمِيعٌ مُّنتَصِرٌ",["Or do they say: We are a host allied together to help each other?","Atau mereka mengatakan, “Kami ini golongan yang bersatu yang pasti menang.”"],530,27,53,212,null,null],[45,4891,"54:45","سَيُهْزَمُ الْجَمْعُ وَيُوَلُّونَ الدُّبُرَ",["Soon shall the hosts be routed, and they shall turn (their) backs.","Golongan itu pasti akan dikalahkan dan mereka akan mundur ke belakang."],530,27,53,212,null,null],[46,4892,"54:46","بَلِ السَّاعَةُ مَوْعِدُهُمْ وَالسَّاعَةُ أَدْهَىٰ وَأَمَرُّ",["Nay, the hour is their promised time, and the hour shall be most grievous and bitter.","Bahkan hari Kiamat itulah hari yang dijanjikan kepada mereka dan hari Kiamat itu lebih dahsyat dan lebih pahit."],530,27,53,212,null,null],[47,4893,"54:47","إِنَّ الْمُجْرِمِينَ فِي ضَلَالٍ وَسُعُرٍ",["Surely the guilty are in error and distress.","Sungguh, orang-orang yang berdosa berada dalam kesesatan (di dunia) dan akan berada dalam neraka (di akhirat)."],530,27,53,212,null,null],[48,4894,"54:48","يَوْمَ يُسْحَبُونَ فِي النَّارِ عَلَىٰ وُجُوهِهِمْ ذُوقُوا مَسَّ سَقَرَ",["On the day when they shall be dragged upon their faces into the fire; taste the touch of hell.","Pada hari mereka diseret ke neraka pada wajahnya. (Dikatakan kepada mereka), “Rasakanlah sentuhan api neraka.”"],530,27,53,212,null,null],[49,4895,"54:49","إِنَّا كُلَّ شَيْءٍ خَلَقْنَاهُ بِقَدَرٍ",["Surely We have created everything according to a measure.","Sungguh, Kami menciptakan segala sesuatu menurut ukuran."],530,27,53,212,null,null],[50,4896,"54:50","وَمَا أَمْرُنَا إِلَّا وَاحِدَةٌ كَلَمْحٍ بِالْبَصَرِ",["And Our command is but one, as the twinkling of an eye.","Dan perintah Kami hanyalah (dengan) satu perkataan seperti kejapan mata."],531,27,53,212,null,null],[51,4897,"54:51","وَلَقَدْ أَهْلَكْنَا أَشْيَاعَكُمْ فَهَلْ مِن مُّدَّكِرٍ",["And certainly We have already destroyed the likes of you, but is there anyone who will mind?","Dan sungguh, telah Kami binasakan orang yang serupa dengan kamu (kekafirannya). Maka adakah orang yang mau mengambil pelajaran?"],531,27,53,212,null,null],[52,4898,"54:52","وَكُلُّ شَيْءٍ فَعَلُوهُ فِي الزُّبُرِ",["And everything they have done is in the writings.","Dan segala sesuatu yang telah mereka perbuat tercatat dalam buku-buku catatan."],531,27,53,212,null,null],[53,4899,"54:53","وَكُلُّ صَغِيرٍ وَكَبِيرٍ مُّسْتَطَرٌ",["And everything small and great is written down.","Dan segala (sesuatu) yang kecil maupun yang besar (semuanya) tertulis."],531,27,53,212,null,null],[54,4900,"54:54","إِنَّ الْمُتَّقِينَ فِي جَنَّاتٍ وَنَهَرٍ",["Surely those who guard (against evil) shall be in gardens and rivers,","Sungguh, orang-orang yang bertakwa berada di taman-taman dan sungai-sungai,"],531,27,53,212,null,null],[55,4901,"54:55","فِي مَقْعَدِ صِدْقٍ عِندَ مَلِيكٍ مُّقْتَدِرٍ",["In the seat of honor with a most Powerful King.","di tempat yang disenangi di sisi Tuhan Yang Mahakuasa."],531,27,53,212,null,null]],[[[1,11,528,"&#xfbac;","word","اقْتَرَبَتِ",["Has come near",""]],[2,11,528,"&#xfbad;","word","السَّاعَةُ",["the Hour",""]],[3,11,528,"&#xfbae;","word","وَانْشَقَّ",["and has split",""]],[4,11,5